// INTEGRATE THE GLOBAL DECLARATION OF INTEGRITY_INFORMATION_SCENARIO

// **** double cannot influence the model logic (they are skipped when checking the model) ****
// distance: in cm
// time step: 0.1 second
// velocity: in m/s = 10cm/0.1s
// acceleration: in m/s²= cm/(0.1s)²


